casebody.data:
DIONYSIA E. TSERIONI ET AL. v. THE UNITED STATES [No. 45214]

[Ante, p. 142; 314 U. S. —]

Import duties; determination by board and liquidation conclusive; statute of limitation.

Decided June 2, 1941; defendant’s demurrer sustained and petition dismissed.

Plaintiffs’ petition for writ of certiorari denied by the Supreme Court October 20, 1941.
